ition:relative;\"><a href=\"#5%EB%8B%A8%EA%B3%84-vitest-%EC%97%85%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8\" aria-label=\"5단계 vitest 업데이트 permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>5단계: Vitest 업데이트</h3>\n<p>Vitest를 사용하는 경우 3.2 이상으로 업데이트:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"json\"><pre class=\"language-json\"><code class=\"language-json\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">\"devDependencies\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token property\">\"vitest\"</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"^3.2.0\"</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"새로운-기능\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%83%88%EB%A1%9C%EC%9A%B4-%EA%B8%B0%EB%8A%A5\" aria-label=\"새로운 기능 permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>새로운 기능</h2>\n<h3 id=\"1-rolldown-통합-실험적\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-rolldown-%ED%86%B5%ED%95%A9-%EC%8B%A4%ED%97%98%EC%A0%81\" aria-label=\"1 rolldown 통합 실험적 permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1. Rolldown 통합 (실험적)</h3>\n<p>Rust 기반의 새로운 번들러 Rolldown이 실험적으로 통합되었습니다.</p>\n<p><strong>사용 방법:</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"bash\"><pre class=\"language-bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">npm</span> <span class=\"token function\">install</span> --save-dev rolldown-vite</code></pre></div>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// vite.config.js</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> defineConfig <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'vite'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">import</span> rolldown <span class=\"token keyword\">from</span> <span class=\"token string\">'rolldown-vite'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token function\">defineConfig</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token literal-property property\">plugins</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token function\">rolldown</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p><strong>장점:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>더 빠른 빌드 시간 (특히 대규모 프로젝트)</li>\n<li>향후 기본 번들러로 채택 예정</li>\n<li>Rust의 성능 이점 활용</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"2-buildapp-훅\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#2-buildapp-%ED%9B%85\" aria-label=\"2 buildapp 훅 permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>2. buildApp 훅</h3>\n<p>새로운 <code class=\"language-text\">buildApp</code> 훅으로 플러그인 개발자는 환경별 빌드를 더 세밀하게 제어할 수 있습니다:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// 플러그인 예시</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">export</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">default</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span> <span class=\"token function\">myPlugin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">name</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'my-plugin'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">buildApp</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      <span class=\"token function\">handler</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">options</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// 환경별 빌드 로직</span>\n        console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Building environments:'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> options<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>environments<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2 id=\"생태계-업데이트\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%83%9D%ED%83%9C%EA%B3%84-%EC%97%85%EB%8D%B0%EC%9D%B4%ED%8A%B8\" aria-label=\"생태계 업데이트 permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>생태계 업데이트</h2>\n<h3 id=\"viteconf-2025\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#viteconf-2025\" aria-label=\"viteconf 2025 permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>ViteConf 2025</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>최초의 오프라인 ViteConf가 암스테르담에서 개최(10월 9일 ~ 10일)</li>\n<li>Vite 생태계의 성장과 커뮤니티 활성화</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"vite-devtools\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#vite-devtools\" aria-label=\"vite devtools permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Vite DevTools</h3>\n<p>VoidZero와 NuxtLabs가 협력하여 개발 중인 새로운 개발 도구:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>향상된 디버깅 경험</li>\n<li>성능 프로파일링</li>\n<li>플러그인 인사이트</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"문서-번역\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%84%9C-%EB%B2%88%EC%97%AD\" aria-label=\"문서 번역 permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문서 번역</h3>\n<p>페르시아어(فارسی) 문서 번역이 추가되어 더 많은 개발자가 Vite를 접할 수 있게 되었습니다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"마무리\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%A7%88%EB%AC%B4%EB%A6%AC\" aria-label=\"마무리 permalink\" class=\"custom-class before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" height=\"20\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"20\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>마무리</h2>\n<p>Vite 7.0은 성능, 현대성, 개발자 경험을 개선하는 중요한 업데이트입니다. Node.js 요구사항 변경과 일부 deprecated 기능 제거가 있지만, 전반적으로 Vite 6에서 부드러운 마이그레이션이 가능합니다.</p>\n<p><strong>주요 체크리스트:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>✅ Node.js 20.19+ 또는 22.12+ 업그레이드</li>\n<li>✅ 브라우저 타겟 검토</li>\n<li>✅ Deprecated 기능 제거</li>\n<li>✅ Vitest 3.2+ 업데이트 (해당 시)</li>\n<li>✅ Rolldown 실험적 기능 테스트 (선택사항)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>자세한 마이그레이션 가이드는 <a href=\"https://vite.dev/guide/migration\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\">공식 문서</a>를 참조하세요.</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Vite 7.0","date":"2025.09.07","category":"개발","tags":["bundler"]},"tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"#vite-70-%EC%B6%9C%EC%8B%9C-%EC%A3%BC%EC%9A%94-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD-%EB%B0%8F-%EB%A7%88%EC%9D%B4%EA%B7%B8%EB%A0%88%EC%9D%B4%EC%85%98-%EA%B0%80%EC%9D%B4%EB%93%9C\">Vite 7.0 출시: 주요 변경사항 및 마이그레이션 가이드</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#-%EB%AA%A9%EC%B0%A8\">📋 목차</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%A3%BC%EC%9A%94-%EB%B3%80%EA%B2%BD%EC%82%AC%ED%95%AD\">주요 변경사항</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#vite-60%EA%B3%BC-%EB%B9%84%EA%B5%90\">Vite 6.0과 비교</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EB%A7%88%EC%9D%B4%EA%B7%B8%EB%A0%88%EC%9D%B4%EC%85%98-%EA%B0%80%EC%9D%B4%EB%93%9C\">마이그레이션 가이드</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%83%88%EB%A1%9C%EC%9A%B4-%EA%B8%B0%EB%8A%A5\">새로운 기능</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"#%EC%83%9D%ED%83%9C%EA%B3%84-%EC%97%85%EB%8D%B0%EC%